### Get All Vendors
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors

### Get Vendor Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}

### Update Vendor Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isOpen": false
}

### Get Vendor Menu
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu

### Get Available Menu Items Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/available

### Get Menu Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/categories

### Create Menu Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Pad Thai",
  "price": 12.99,
  "isAvailable": true,
  "category": "Main Course"
}

### Create Another Menu Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Spring Rolls",
  "price": 6.99,
  "isAvailable": true,
  "category": "Appetizer"
}

### Get Specific Menu Item
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/{{menuItemId}}

### Update Menu Item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/{{menuItemId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Pad Thai (Updated)",
  "price": 13.99,
  "isAvailable": true,
  "category": "Main Course"
}

### Toggle Menu Item Availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/{{menuItemId}}/availability
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isAvailable": false
}

### Batch Toggle Availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vendors/{{vendorId}}/menu/batch/availability
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [7, 8],
  "isAvailable": false
}

